      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="4489th">4489th meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2002-03-12" refersTo="#adoptionDate">12 March 2002</docDate></docTitle>
